{"tid":373832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又一單！呃逾9萬元綜援　86歲翁罪成還押候判","createTime":"2017-08-25T10:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T10:16:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7ebc91ed78fb6c3ccb180d909ef92d460f171e","tid":373832,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"86歲獨居老翁陳庚富被指在申領綜援後，未有申報姪女於2008年至2013年間月付1500至4000港元的收入。陳因而涉多申領9萬多港元的綜援，案件今日(25日)在粉嶺法院審理，被告被裁定罪成，裁判官將他還押至9月8日判刑，期間索取其背景報告，同時了解其還款情況。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁決指，接納控方證人，即社署職員和警員是誠實可靠的證人。裁判官又指被告辯稱只是忘記申報，但事實上他自2008年起已接受姪女資助，每次姪女存款後，他很快便會將錢提走，故不接納其説法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170825/bkn-20170825151548002-0825_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170825%2Fbkn-20170825151548002-0825_00822_001.html&d=xFKPCRVVs%2F3NYMp6016aKDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=70ab60d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170825/bkn-20170825151548002-0825_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"66e0090a179ac615d73646127d8c1739deea75ed","tid":373832,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"你瘋狂開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要call多幾個手足增援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6429aef3c0d1c27ff9ddef9ae02f82ca79728","tid":373832,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"阿伯好慘 想捐錢比佢"},{"pid":"5633438d5b9690d626a859ca83a8200cb8025e0e","tid":373832,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}